<br>
I wouldn't ever change the pledge to what you said simply because I would feel like I'm accepting &quot;justice for some&quot; rather than &quot;justice for all.&quot;  Something that goes against our constitution.  I think there is justice for all in this country though, I'm curious as to where you think there is a lack of justice.  Mind sharing? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
